{"tid":697133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"〔高登64  集體失憶〕613慘案五週年","createTime":"2018-06-10T16:56:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T16:48:02.000Z","uid":22675,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c379bdc481e11f3518aaa02607465c2e2b11331b","tid":697133,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:56:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img4.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20130614152729/evchk/images/d/dc/Housenews_613_bam.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg4.wikia.nocookie.net%2F__cb20130614152729%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fd%2Fdc%2FHousenews_613_bam.jpg&h=8d485891&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n613大量高登會員被封禁事件，又稱613大屠殺事件、613事件，是繼1028高登大量會員被封禁事件後第二次高登版的六四事件，發生於2013年6月13日，當日有大量高登會員發現自己帳號被封禁（BAM），肇事會員已超過500人，刪post至少400多個，為高登有紀錄以來封禁最多人及刪post最多的一次。期間一眾被封禁會員紛紛借用其它高登帳號，上站務台質問高登管理員。 <br />\n<br />\n林祖舜事後在「高登公告」證實，大規模封禁會員是與會員對某傳媒企業的言論或涉誹謗有關。 <br />\n<br />\n613慘案wiki <br />\n<a href=\"http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/613%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E9%AB%98%E7%99%BB%E6%9C%83%E5%93%A1%E8%A2%AB%E5%B0%81%E7%A6%81%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2F613%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2587%258F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E7%2599%25BB%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25B0%2581%25E7%25A6%2581%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6&d=7dik%2B57InS7eQz7adFhe%2FQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=23d384bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/613%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E9%AB%98%E7%99%BB%E6%9C%83%E5%93%A1%E8%A2%AB%E5%B0%81%E7%A6%81%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6</a>"},{"pid":"58b720dbb1402dba0c003252aa8eaf49524a5a9d","tid":697133,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:58:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">秒秒鐘賣過百份既東方報業集團支持高登林主席</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20120308/photo/0308-00176-099b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20120308%2Fphoto%2F0308-00176-099b2.jpg&h=b807a795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 　<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">多謝方丈聲援白色恐怖</span></strong>　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20140529/photo/0529-00176-065b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140529%2Fphoto%2F0529-00176-065b4.jpg&h=4824277c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n誹謗東方實捉到你　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「犯東方者，雖難必誅，雖遠亦必誅！」東方報業集團近年屢遭網上誹謗貼文攻擊，數目已逾千宗。東方不惜花費人力物力，誓要揪出發放誹謗貼文的網民及幕後黑手，以向有關人士採取法律行動。討論區Games Animation Forum過去多年多次出現涉嫌誹謗東方及其管理層的貼文，經東方於二○一一年入稟控告該網站的註冊人／登記人李偉文後，李今日就事件刊登道歉啟事及表示有關貼文帶有嚴重貶義，並向受影響人士道歉及作出賠償。而在「明報網站」內的「亞洲週刊討論區」，發布涉嫌誹謗貼文的網民亦已原形畢露，並已就事件向東方作出書面道歉，表示「知道了自己的錯誤，內心十分後悔」，並承諾不會再轉載沒有事實根據的貼文。資訊科技界及法律界均指，互聯網的誹謗貼文並非無迹可尋，呼籲網民切勿以身試法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20140529/00176_065.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140529%2F00176_065.html&d=7dik%2B57InS7eQz7adFhe%2FQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=5a11a8f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20140529/00176_065.html</a>"},{"pid":"7a17d3d7cc74cd32f8166fc80c12bdd8d6ab5700","tid":697133,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:01:54.000Z","msg":"追究屠城責任!!!!!!!!!!!!!林祖舜專政!!!!!!!!!!!!!!建設民主高登!!!!!!!!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n每年識得笑支那國班人連六四係咩都唔知 <br />\n<br />\n但高登仔自己連林早洩喺上年613　因為百份報亂bam人都聲都唔聲 <br />\n<br />\n莫講話做　連講都唔敢講"},{"pid":"ff116159ad9a72afd693ec29304d5e007ac37a4f","tid":697133,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86660d21b43ea07eda447b1c20e04c49696b4834","tid":697133,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike"